### Upload a single image to R2
POST http://localhost:8081/api/media/upload
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=--------------------------boundary123

----------------------------boundary123
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="image"; filename="blur.jpg"
Content-Type: image/jpeg

< ../test-file/blur.jpg
----------------------------boundary123--


### Upload a single image to R2
GET http://localhost:8081/api/media/sign-url
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "key":"123.png"
}
###
GET http://localhost:8081/api/media?page=1
Content-Type: application/json

###
GET http://localhost:8081/api/media?page=1&excludes=1
Content-Type: application/json

###
GET http://localhost:8081/api/media-id?ids=1
Content-Type: application/json

### Update metadata
PUT  http://localhost:8081/api/media/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
    
    "metadata":{
        "name":"123.png",
        "size":"123",
        "type":"image/png",
        "url":"https://example.com/123.png"
    }
}